page_title: 'Quickstart - Get started using Provisioned Deployments with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started provisioned deployments on Azure OpenAI Service.
chunk_content: Understanding expected throughputThe amount of throughput that you can achieve on the endpoint is a factor of the number of PTUs deployed, input size, output size and call rate. The number of concurrent calls and total tokens processed can vary based on these values. Our recommended way for determining the throughput for your deployment is as follows:1.	Use the Capacity calculator for a sizing estimate. You can find the capacity calculator in the Azure OpenAI Studio under the quotas page and Provisioned tab.  2.	Benchmark the load using real traffic workload. For more information about benchmarking, see the benchmarking section.
